OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,FDonald Trump has claimed he and
OL,7,FChinese President Xi Jinping "feel
OL,8,Fvery similar" about how the war in
OL,9,FIran should end, as he wrapped up his
OL,10,Fofficial state visit to Beijing.
OL,12,FThe US president said he and Xi
OL,13,F"settled a lot of different problems
OL,14,Fthat other people wouldn't have been
OL,15,Fable to settle" and "made some
OL,16,Ffantastic trade deals", as the two
OL,17,Fleaders spoke at a bilateral meeting
OL,18,Fon Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,F"We did discuss Iran. We feel very
OL,7,Fsimilar (about) Iran, we want that to
OL,8,Fend and we don't want them to have a
OL,9,Fnuclear weapon," Trump said.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,F"We want the straits open (...) and we
OL,17,Fwant them to get it ended because it's
OL,18,Fa crazy thing. They're a little bit
OL,19,Fcrazy and that's no good. Can't have
OL,20,Fit. They cannot have a nuclear weapon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,F"But we discussed a lot of other
OL,7,Fthings also and I think we're very
OL,8,Fmuch on agreement."
OL,10,FTrump went on to thank Xi and state
OL,11,Fthat the Chinese president would be
OL,12,Fcoming to the US in late September.
OL,14,F"We're going to lay it on the line,
OL,15,Fand hopefully you're going to walk
OL,16,Faway very impressed, like I am very
OL,17,Fimpressed with China," Trump said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,FThe US president and Xi spoke from
OL,7,FZhongnanhai, the leadership compound
OL,8,Ffor the Chinese Communist Party, which
OL,9,Fis often thought of as the nation's
OL,10,Fequivalent to the White House and has
OL,11,Faround 1,500 acres of grounds.
OL,13,FThe two leaders had lunch together
OL,14,Fafter the meeting, and Trump boarded
OL,15,FAir Force One to return to the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,FReflecting on the visit, Xi said he
OL,7,Fand Trump had "defined a new position
OL,8,Ffor a constructive strategic and
OL,9,Fstable relationship" between China and
OL,10,Fthe US and had established "deepening
OL,11,Fmutual trust".
OL,13,F"This also once again shows that China
OL,14,Fand the United States are willing to
OL,15,Fachieve peaceful coexistence, win-win
OL,16,Fcooperation on the basis of mutual
OL,17,Frespect and find a right way to get
OL,18,Falong," Xi said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
