FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,FTrump had previously stated that Xi
OL,7,Fsaid China wanted to help negotiate an
OL,8,Fend to the war in Iran and the
OL,9,Freopening of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,10,Fwhich has been almost entirely closed
OL,11,Fsince March.
OL,13,FChina is the largest buyer of Iranian
OL,14,Foil, and Trump is hopeful the
OL,15,Fpresident can use that leverage to
OL,16,Fconvince Iran to make a deal on US
OL,17,Fterms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,FIn a statement, China's foreign
OL,7,Fministry said there was "no
OL,8,Fjustification" for the war to
OL,9,Fcontinue, noting that it is "important
OL,10,Fto reopen the shipping lanes as soon
OL,11,Fas possible".
OL,13,F"China's position on the situation in
OL,14,FIran is very clear. This conflict has
OL,15,Falready caused severe losses to the
OL,16,Fpeople of countries in the region,
OL,17,Fincluding Iran, and its spillover
OL,18,Feffects continue to expand," it said
OL,19,Fon Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,F"It has seriously disrupted global
OL,7,Feconomic development, the smooth
OL,8,Foperation of production and supply
OL,9,Fchains, the international trade order
OL,10,Fand the stability of global energy
OL,11,Fsupplies, and has harmed the common
OL,12,Finterests of the international
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,15,F"There is no justification for this
OL,16,Fconflict, which should never have
OL,17,Foccurred, to continue. Finding a
OL,18,Fsolution as soon as possible would be
OL,19,Fin the interests of both the US and
OL,20,FIran, as well as the countries in the
OL,21,Fregion and the world at large."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778861473
OL,3,CTrump says US and China 'feel very
OL,4,Csimilar' on how Iran war should end
OL,6,FThe statement came hours after Trump
OL,7,Fdeclared that the "military decimation
OL,8,Fof Iran" was "to be continued" in a
OL,9,Fpost on Truth Social, in which he
OL,10,Fclaimed Xi had declared Biden's
OL,11,FAmerica "a declining nation".
OL,13,F"When President Xi very elegantly
OL,14,Freferred to the United States as
OL,15,Fperhaps being a declining nation, he
OL,16,Fwas referring to the tremendous damage
OL,17,Fwe suffered during the four years of
OL,18,FSleepy Joe Biden and the Biden
OL,19,FAdministration, and on that score, he
OL,20,Fwas 100% correct," Trump said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
